In this project I'm going to map the public parks in my town - Hod Hasharon, and check their surrounding environment. For this I'll use two OSM layers - `leisure: park` and `landuse: [all]`. Intersecting a buffer zone around the parks with the landuse layer, will map the area surrounding the parks.

